title: "ralph-vault: a progressive-disclosure knowledge vault skill"
abstract: >-
  A Python CLI tool / library to create and maintain a progressive-disclosure
  knowledge vault (a tiered "deepwiki") for one or many code repositories — the
  knowledge source for LLM / AI agent loops (ralph-style).
